Package: qlcheckr
Title: Helpful Code Checking for Quarto Live
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mitchell",
           family = "O'Hara-Wild",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mail@mitchelloharawild.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6729-7695"))
Description: Provides a framework for interactive code checking in Quarto Live. 
    The package enables users to define logical tests for code correctness, 
    delivers custom feedback messages, and includes debugging capabilities 
    to display evaluation details and error hints. Designed to enhance 
    teaching, learning, and automated code assessment workflows.
